{"data":[{"date":"15:25 08/08","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb9p c\u00f3 ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i?","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/nguoi-dep-co-phat-ngon-gay-soc-la-ban-gai-moi-cua-tien-ve-trong-dai.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"5250","checkdouble":"194035"},{"date":"17:32 08/08","title":"B\u00e0o ch\u1eefa v\u1ee5 coi th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Conte, Willian tr\u00e1ch con g\u00e1i","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/8/bao-chua-vu-coi-thuong-thay-cu-conte-willian-trach-con-gai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Chelsea, Willian \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00e1ch c\u00f4 con g\u00e1i y\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i v\u1ec1 HLV Conte.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Man United gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch FA Cup 2017/18, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Chelsea, Willian \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh The Blues n\u00e2ng C\u00fap \u0111\u1ec3 \u0103n m\u1eebng tr\u00ean Instagram.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nWillian \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c khi \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh \u0103n m\u1eebng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh HLV Conte b\u1ecb che k\u00edn ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1eb1ng 3 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng C\u00fap V\u00e0ng. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng coi th\u01b0\u1eddng Conte c\u1ee7a Willian.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/NINTCHDBPICT000425311293_2018080810242517.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, trong cu\u1ed9c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n tr\u00ean ESPN Brasil v\u00e0o h\u00f4m qua, Willian kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea5y C\u00fap che m\u1eb7t Conte trong b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i n\u00f3i tr\u00ean. Ng\u00f4i sao Brazil cho hay, ch\u00ednh c\u00f4 con g\u00e1i y\u00eau c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCon g\u00e1i t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u1ecbch \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u00e0 g\u1eafn nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00ean m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Conte.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean chuy\u1ebfn bay v\u1ec1 Brazil. Khi t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea v\u00e0o s\u00e1ng h\u00f4m sau, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh l\u00ean m\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0103n m\u1eebng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u00f3 (Conte b\u1ecb che m\u1eb7t) v\u00ec qu\u00e1 m\u1ec7t\u201d, Willian cho hay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 b\u00e0o ch\u1eefa cho ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh v\u00ec \u201ctai n\u1ea1n\u201d n\u00f3i tr\u00ean nh\u01b0ng Willian m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa c\u00f4ng khai b\u00e0y t\u1ecf b\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Conte, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Brazil thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Willian c\u00f4ng k\u00edch Conte \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e0nh x\u1eed kh\u00f4ng chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, khi\u1ebfn The Blues m\u1ea5t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat quan tr\u1ecdng Diego Costa.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5249","checkdouble":"194041"},{"date":"15:20 08/08","title":"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft: \"T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/9/5/van-quyet-toi-da-no-luc-de-duoc-tham-du-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh V\u0103n L\u00e2m thay v\u00ec V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 tranh c\u00e3i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft chia s\u1ebb sau khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD.\r\n</h2><h2><br />\r\nV\u0103n Quy\u1ebft &ldquo;tho\u00e1t hi\u1ec3m&rdquo; ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u k\u00e9m \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 g\u1eb7p Uzbekistan, nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u1eabn c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t &ndash; \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m l\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf nh\u00e0. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ra s\u1ef1 tranh c\u00e3i l\u1edbn.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 1 su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i. Anh cho bi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Zing: &ldquo;L\u00e0 1 trong 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1eeb c\u00e1c ph\u00eda. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c BHL \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00fang m\u1ef1c.&rdquo;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft chia s\u1ebb sau khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD\" title=\"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/82-1533604846.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft chia s\u1ebb sau khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n&ldquo;T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. Tr\u00ean h\u1ebft, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng, v\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i. Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft, g\u1ed3m nh\u1eefng m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p nh\u1ecf h\u1ee3p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi nhau. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m v\u00e0 \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1ea3i ASIAD ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc.&rdquo;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn trong danh s\u00e1ch, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m chi\u1ebfc b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Cho d\u00f9 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a anh trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p U23 Uzbekistan l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, nh\u01b0ng HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh to\u00e1n c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang \u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft chia s\u1ebb sau khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u00e1p l\u1ef1c h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda anh l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-khi-van-lam-bi-loai-khoi-asiad-472-194022.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-khi-van-lam-bi-loai-khoi-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-khi-van-lam-bi-loai-khoi-asiad-472-194022.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi ASIAD</span><br />\r\nTh\u00f4ng tin th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng bongda24h t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u k\u1ebb th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-chon-van-quyet-gat-van-lam-con-dao-hai-luoi-168-193982.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/hlv-park-hang-seo-chon-van-quyet-gat-van-lam-con-dao-hai-luoi.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-chon-van-quyet-gat-van-lam-con-dao-hai-luoi-168-193982.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ecdn V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, g\u1ea1t V\u0103n L\u00e2m: L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn?</span><br />\r\nD\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ea1ng nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111ang b\u00e0n t\u00e1n x\u00f4n xao v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic c\u1ee7a HLV...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5248","checkdouble":"194032"},{"date":"15:44 08/08","title":"\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0\" \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft c\u1ee7a Park Hang Seo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/27/nguoi-nha-ung-ho-quyet-dinh-lua-chon-van-quyet-cua-park-hang-seo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u2013 HLV Ph\u1ea1m Minh \u0110\u1ee9c chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nV\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c &ldquo;ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0&rdquo; tin t\u01b0\u1edfng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft. \u00dd ki\u1ebfn n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i tr\u00e1i chi\u1ec1u, r\u1eb1ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 qua.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y, Ph\u1ea1m Minh \u0110\u1ee9c cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;N\u00f3i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea9ng c\u1ea5p. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n l\u00e2u r\u1ed3i, l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng, t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1ea1y b\u00e9n. V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Uzbekistan l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t r\u1ed3i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn to\u00e0n th\u1ec3, tr\u00e1nh phi\u1ebfn di\u1ec7n. Danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn 3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u01a1n tu\u1ed5i, V\u0103n L\u00e2m c\u0169ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft c\u0169ng v\u1eady. M\u1ed7i m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i tr\u00e1i chi\u1ec1u, v\u00e0 HLV s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m. D\u00f9 sao, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00ec d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn m\u00e0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ph\u1ea1m Minh \u0110\u1ee9c chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD\" title=\"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/27/nguoi-nha-ung-ho-quyet-dinh-lua-chon-van-quyet-cua-park-hang-seo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ph\u1ea1m Minh \u0110\u1ee9c chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;\u00d4ng Park \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean \u00f4ng \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecdn ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1edf. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, ASIAD c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a di\u1ec5n ra, sao c\u1ee9 l\u00f4i V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft ra tranh c\u00e3i? CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1edfi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecdn h\u1ecd th\u00ec ch\u1ecdn ai b\u00e2y gi\u1edd? Hi\u1ec7n nay HAGL, Viettel hay SLNA kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng Park kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn danh s\u00e1ch.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;D\u00f9 sao, vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 theo b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ai. \u00d4ng Park l\u00e0 HLV \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, v\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 l\u00fd do c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u1ec1 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t t\u1eeb x\u01b0a nay, qua bao \u0111\u1eddi HLV r\u1ed3i. C\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y danh s\u00e1ch 20 ng\u01b0\u1eddi cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. Ch\u00fang ta \u00edt nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd v\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Ph\u1ea1m Minh \u0110\u1ee9c chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-khi-van-lam-bi-loai-khoi-asiad-472-194022.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-khi-van-lam-bi-loai-khoi-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-khi-van-lam-bi-loai-khoi-asiad-472-194022.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi ASIAD</span><br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng tin th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng bongda24h t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u k\u1ebb th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-chon-van-quyet-gat-van-lam-con-dao-hai-luoi-168-193982.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/hlv-park-hang-seo-chon-van-quyet-gat-van-lam-con-dao-hai-luoi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-chon-van-quyet-gat-van-lam-con-dao-hai-luoi-168-193982.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ecdn V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, g\u1ea1t V\u0103n L\u00e2m: L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn?</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ea1ng nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111ang b\u00e0n t\u00e1n x\u00f4n xao v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic c\u1ee7a HLV...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/van-quyet-toi-da-no-luc-de-duoc-tham-du-asiad-472-194032.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/9/5/van-quyet-toi-da-no-luc-de-duoc-tham-du-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/van-quyet-toi-da-no-luc-de-duoc-tham-du-asiad-472-194032.html\">V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft: T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD</span><br>\r\nQuy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh V\u0103n L\u00e2m thay v\u00ec V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 tranh c\u00e3i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft chia s\u1ebb sau khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5247","checkdouble":"194036"},{"date":"15:25 08/08","title":"M.U \u0111\u00f3n tin m\u1eebng trong v\u1ee5 s\u0103n \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/22/bayern-khong-muon-mua-ante-rebic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Bayern kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n mua Ante Rebic. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cho Man United s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh m\u1edbi c\u00f9ng \u0110T Croatia l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M.U t\u00ednh mua Rebic</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Ante Rebic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Croatia ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t. Anh c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Balkan l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi chung k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRebic mang nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i \u1edf t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean ti\u1ec1n tuy\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ch\u1ea1y hai c\u00e1nh t\u1edbi trung phong. S\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn 24 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 c\u00e0n l\u01b0\u1edbt v\u00e0 x\u1eed l\u00fd tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bayern kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n mua Ante Rebic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Bayern kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n mua Ante Rebic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/bayern-khong-muon-mua-ante-rebic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Rebic ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t m\u00e0 HLV Jose Mourinho c\u1ee7a Man United \u01b0a th\u00edch. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean m\u00e0 c\u00f3 tin Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean r\u00fat lui</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAi c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 Bayern Munich s\u1ebd nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Ante Rebic v\u00e0 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 HLV Niko Kovac, th\u1ea7y c\u0169 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i Eintracht Frankfurt. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u00f4ng qua ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Bayern, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Rebic.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-du-dinh-chi-50-trieu-bang-mua-rebic-172-192000.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/mu-du-dinh-chi-50-trieu-bang-mua-rebic.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-du-dinh-chi-50-trieu-bang-mua-rebic-172-192000.html\">MU d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua sao Croatia</span><br>\r\n<span>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Ante Rebic c\u1ee7a Eintracht Frankfurt, theo Sport Bild, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec gi\u1eefa Bayern v\u00e0 Ante Rebic&rdquo;, Kovac n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Sport Bild. &ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec trong chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. H\u00f4m nay kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec v\u00e0 ng\u00e0y mai c\u0169ng v\u1eady.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Bayern kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n mua Ante Rebic l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 tin vui v\u1edbi M.U. HLV Mourinho c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. M.U t\u1eebng nh\u1eafm Gareth Bale c\u1ee7a Real Madrid v\u00e0 Ivan Perisic c\u1ee7a Inter Milan song kh\u00f4ng \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-khung-bayern-chinh-thuc-tu-choi-man-united-172-194011.html\">M.U nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c bu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb sao kh\u1ee7ng Bayern</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-da-dong-y-ban-trung-ve-khung-cho-mu-172-193988.html\">Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng cho M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-dau-hieu-cuc-lon-cho-thay-mu-chuan-bi-don-trung-ve-moi-172-193882.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn cho th\u1ea5y M.U chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/willian-chinh-thuc-dua-ra-cau-tra-loi-cho-mu-barca-172-193877.html\">Willian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho M.U, Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-boateng-voi-mu-172-193871.html\">Arsenal gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh sao tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi M.U</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5246","checkdouble":"194033"},{"date":"15:31 08/08","title":"Sao kh\u1ee7ng Barca ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/8/dembele-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u01b0a tin ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ousmane Dembele s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn t\u1eeb Arsenal v\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barcelona th\u00eam m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u1eefa.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kh\u00e1 t\u1ec7 t\u1ea1i Camp Nou. D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 135.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng Dembele thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/dembele-muon-chay-tron-khoi-barca-180-191966.html\" target=\"_blank\">ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Dembele s\u1ebd chia tay Barca</span>. Anh c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng cho su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1nh Malcom h\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Dembele ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Dembele ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/dembele-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Ousmane Dembele t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00f4m th\u1ee9 Ba v\u1eeba qua, c\u00f3 tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Dembele v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Emirates. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Arsenal s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc 8.9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Dembele. N\u1ebfu ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1ebd mua \u0111\u1ee9t anh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng theo t\u1edd Mundo Deportivo, Dembele \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Josep Maria Bartomeu c\u1ee7a Barca. V\u00e0 anh \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn b\u00e0y t\u1ecf nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng \u1edf l\u1ea1i Camp Nou th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Dembele \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m d\u1ea5y l\u00ean tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal sau khi c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i \u0103n t\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean l\u00e0 Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang v\u00e0 Henrikh Mkhitaryan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Unai Emery r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1c:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-chi-tiet-hop-dong-courtois-sap-ky-voi-real-madrid-172-194030.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Chi ti\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng Courtois s\u1eafp k\u00fd v\u1edbi Real Madrid?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hazard-va-giroud-muon-chelsea-mua-nabil-fekir-172-194029.html\">Hazard v\u00e0 Giroud mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5245","checkdouble":"194031"},{"date":"14:59 08/08","title":"HLV Real kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n so s\u00e1nh Bale v\u00e0 Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/8/hlv-real-khong-muon-so-sanh-bale-va-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Julen Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Gareth Bale. HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n so s\u00e1nh gi\u1eefa hai ng\u00f4i sao b\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bale t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i Real</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u00e1ng nay, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc AS Roma t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, ng\u00f4i sao Gareth Bale tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n m\u00e0 Los Blancos ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, anh vu\u1ed1t m\u00e1 ngo\u00e0i ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Marco Asensio ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh k\u1ebft th\u00fac th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi Juventus c\u0169ng t\u1ea1i ICC, Bale \u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 Wales l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u1edbi Real sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi ch\u00ednh Juventus gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Julen Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Gareth Bale h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Julen Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Gareth Bale h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/hlv-real-khong-muon-so-sanh-bale-va-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Gareth Bale t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong 2 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Lopetegui kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u00e1p l\u1ef1c cho Bale</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale, Julen Lopetegui b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 vui m\u1eebng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ea5t th\u00eam \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u00ean vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. \u201cC\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 thay th\u1ebf m\u1ed9t ai \u0111\u00f3 ho\u1eb7c kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p vai tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00f3. D\u00f9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d, Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Gareth Bale.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cGareth Bale r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 s\u1ebd nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n so s\u00e1nh, vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00f3 d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00ean vai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi mang l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng Bale kh\u00f4ng g\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean vai. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Bale. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o 2h r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 16/8 t\u1edbi, Real s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid t\u1ea1i Tallinn (Estonia). 4 ng\u00e0y sau, h\u1ecd kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch La Liga m\u00f9a m\u1edbi b\u1eb1ng cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Getafe.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Real Madrid tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-muon-kovacic-172-193958.html\">L\u1ed9 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a Mateo Kovacic \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-dam-bao-tuong-lai-cho-hai-nguoi-hung-world-cup-180-193955.html\">Real Madrid \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai cho hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng World Cup</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/luka-modric-tinh-roi-real-sang-inter-milan-180-193950.html\">V\u00ec \u201cmi\u1ebfng b\u00e1nh\u201d b\u00e9o b\u1edf n\u00e0y, Modric t\u00ednh b\u1ecf Real sang Inter</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/courtois-tu-choi-tro-lai-chelsea-quyet-tam-den-real-bang-duoc-172-193892.html\">Courtois t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Real b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/real-madrid-chot-70-trieu-euro-cho-nguoi-thay-the-modric-172-193890.html\">Real Madrid ch\u1ed1t 70 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Modric</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5244","checkdouble":"194028"},{"date":"16:06 08/08","title":"MU nh\u1eafm sao Barca thay th\u1ebf Luke Shaw","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/27/mu-nham-sao-barca-thay-the-luke-shaw.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1edd Daily Star \u0111\u01b0a tin Man United \u0111ang ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i Jordi Alba \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf cho Luke Shaw.</h2><h2>MU nh\u1eafm Jordi Alba\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jordi Alba\" title=\"Jordi Alba\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/17/mu-nham-sao-barca-nang-cap-hang-thu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>MU nh\u1eafm h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Jordi Alba thay Luke Shaw</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u01afu ti\u00ean ban \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Man United \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho Luke Shaw \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Alex Sandro c\u1ee7a Juventus v\u00e0 Danny Rose c\u1ee7a Tottenham.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Man \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, t\u1edd Daily Star m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0a tin r\u1eb1ng HLV Mourinho \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/jordi-alba-44444.html\" target=\"_blank\">h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Jordi Alba</span> v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTruy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha cho r\u1eb1ng Mourinho mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Alba l\u00e0 b\u1edfi v\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i d\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbng Pep Guardiola t\u1ea1i Barca. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 hy v\u1ecdng nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Alba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u00f4ng t\u00ecm ra c\u00e1ch ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n s\u1ef1 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Man City.</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 kh\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Jordi Alba v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u1ea5p. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng kh\u00e1 \u00eam \u1ea3 t\u1ea1i Camp Nou. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Barca th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n b\u00e1n \u0111i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng cho Alba l\u00e0 Lucas Digne cho Everton.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 gi\u1eefa Shaw v\u00e0 HLV Mourinho c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o nh\u1eefng m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u00e0 Shaw h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a MU trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Luke Shaw th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n nh\u01b0ng Mourinho kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n kh\u00e1c. Premier League s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi tranh trong 2 ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi v\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o 1 c\u00e1i t\u00ean l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Toby Alderweireld m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU&nbsp;kh\u00e1c:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-duc/bayern-khong-muon-mua-ante-rebic-193-194033.html\">M.U \u0111\u00f3n tin m\u1eebng trong v\u1ee5 s\u0103n \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hazard-va-giroud-muon-chelsea-mua-nabil-fekir-172-194029.html\">Hazard v\u00e0 Giroud mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5243","checkdouble":"194037"},{"date":"17:04 08/08","title":"Pep Guardiola: \"Man City s\u1ebd c\u00f2n kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp h\u01a1n n\u1eefa\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/pep-guardiola-man-city-se-con-khung-khiep-hon-nua.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, HLV Pep Guardiola kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City c\u00f2n m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n n\u1eefa so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMan City v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ph\u00e1t huy h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">100 \u0111i\u1ec3m gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i gi\u00fap Man City ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c Premier League, tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch cao \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed. H\u1ecd h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 l\u00e0 Man United t\u1edbi 19 \u0111i\u1ec3m, v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c &ldquo;v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i&rdquo; \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn Community Shield m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea. HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c reo r\u1eafc n\u1ed7i s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i t\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi chia s\u1ebb sau \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Man City s\u1ebd c\u00f2n m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u01a1n, b\u1edfi v\u1eady nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o b\u1eb1ng ch\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i, gi\u1edd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n b\u1eb1ng c\u1ea3 ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i. Khi b\u1ea1n n\u00e2ng cao phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, b\u1ea1n khi\u1ebfn to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1edf n\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pep Guardiola kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City c\u00f2n m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi\" title=\"HLV Pep Guardiola\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/pep-guardiola-man-city-se-con-khung-khiep-hon-nua.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pep Guardiola kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City c\u00f2n m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o hay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o &ndash; t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang l\u00e0m, c\u1ea3 5 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ch\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u1ea1i l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Man City \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. T\u00f4i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man united, Chelsea, Arsenal, Tottenham, Liverpool &ndash; t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn cam go.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, Pep Guardiola kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City c\u00f2n m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ngai v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh &ndash; \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi man United n\u0103m 2009. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Pep c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jesus-phat-bieu-ve-man-city-172-193856.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/jesus-phat-bieu-ve-man-city.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jesus-phat-bieu-ve-man-city-172-193856.html\">&ldquo;Man City v\u1eabn s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i NHA m\u00f9a t\u1edbi&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nGabriel Jesus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Man City sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea t\u1ea1i Community Shield. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 21 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ef1 tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u0103ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-khang-dinh-se-khong-mua-them-nguoi-172-194007.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/pep-khang-dinh-se-khong-mua-them-nguoi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-khang-dinh-se-khong-mua-them-nguoi-172-194007.html\">Pep kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1eddi</span><br>\r\nH\u1ea1n ch\u00f3t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Premier League s\u1ebd k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 N\u0103m, v\u00e0 HLV Pep Guardiola h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City t\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5242","checkdouble":"194039"},{"date":"16:32 08/08","title":"V\u00ec sao Jerome Boateng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi MU?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/vi-sao-jerome-boateng-khong-phai-lua-chon-hoan-hao-voi-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Jerome Boateng c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c. Song th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Boateng kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHai k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 M.U v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 y\u00ean t\u00e2m. \u1ede phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Jerome Boateng Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ea7y r\u1ee7i ro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Jerome Boateng Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ea7y r\u1ee7i ro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/MU-muon-mua-Jerome-Boateng-Thuong-vu-day-rui-ro-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Boateng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-nham-sao-khung-tuyen-duc-nang-cap-hang-thu-172-189082.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU mu\u1ed1n mua Jerome Boateng</span> c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a &ldquo;H\u00f9m x\u00e1m&rdquo; v\u00e0 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c, Mourinho tin r\u1eb1ng kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a anh&nbsp;r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Jerome Boateng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n c\u00f3 19 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Bundesliga v\u1edbi 1.644 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 \u1edf m\u1ee9c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bayern chi ban Boateng voi gia 50 trieu bang\" title=\"Bayern ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Boateng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/boateng-tu-choi-mu-vi-mourinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Boateng ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Boateng ch\u1ec9 t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng 0.8 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat, th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n trung b\u00ecnh 1.1 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n, 2.7 l\u1ea7n ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 0.7 l\u1ea7n ch\u1eb7n c\u00fa s\u00fat/90 ph\u00fat. D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn nh\u01b0ng Boateng c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1.7 l\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng chi\u00ean th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng/tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Boateng ch\u1ec9 \u1edf m\u1ee9c 67%, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t 84%. \u0110\u00f3 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Ch\u00ednh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Bayern Munich s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<h2>Boateng thua xa nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Boateng so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Otamendi ghi ban quyet dinh truoc Man City\" title=\"Otamendi ghi ban quyet dinh truoc Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/11/Hon-MU-15-diem,-Pep-len-tieng-ca-ngoi-sieu-nhan-trong-doi-hinh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Otamendi ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Boateng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNicolas Otamendi c\u1ee7a Man City l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i: \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n trung b\u00ecnh 3.7 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat, cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n con s\u1ed1 2.7 l\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Boateng. T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Otamendi c\u0169ng cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n (85,66% so v\u1edbi 67%).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVirgil Van Dijk c\u0169ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi Boateng. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 6.27 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n/90 ph\u00fat trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Southampton v\u00e0 Liverpool \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2017/18. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1eb7n c\u00fa s\u00fat t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Van Dijk c\u0169ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Boateng (1.8 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat so v\u1edbi 1.1 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAntonio Rudiger g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng so v\u1edbi Boateng \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn: th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 3.6 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn, g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao b\u00ean ph\u00eda Bayern Munich. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n (3.89 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat so v\u1edbi 2.7 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rudiger chi ra van de cua Chelsea\" title=\"Rudiger ch\u1ec9 ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/sao-tuyen-duc-chi-ra-van-de-chelsea-can-khac-phuc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rudiger c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi Boateng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Boateng l\u00e0 Shkokdran Mustafi c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Arsenal \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i: \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n trung b\u00ecnh 6.77 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat, ch\u1eb7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00fa s\u00fat 2.26 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat, v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Boateng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEric Bailly c\u1ee7a M.U ch\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kho\u1ea3ng 1000 ph\u00fat \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2017/18 nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u0169ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi Boateng: \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n 5 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat v\u00e0 ch\u1eb7n c\u00fa s\u00fat 2.25 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat.</div>\r\n<h2>Boateng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a MU?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, Boateng c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 M.U \u0111ang nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham, Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca hay Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Maguire va Toby Alderweireld la nhung muc tieu hang dau cua M.U\" title=\"Harry Maguire v\u00e0 Toby Alderweireld l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/27/vi-sao-mourinho-phai-mua-bang-duoc-trung-ve-khung.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Maguire v\u00e0 Toby Alderweireld v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ea1nh Boateng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Boateng, Alderweireld d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 1.177 ph\u00fat \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, song m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 3.82 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n/90 ph\u00fat v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 3.8 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nYerry Mina ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n 370 ph\u00fat \u1edf La Liga m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1edbi 3.9 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n v\u00e0 1.5 l\u1ea7n ch\u1eb7n c\u00fa s\u00fat/90 ph\u00fat,&nbsp; v\u1eabn t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Boateng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, n\u1ebfu so s\u00e1nh Boateng v\u00e0 Maguire th\u00ec c\u00f2n kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t n\u1eefa. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ra s\u00e2n 3.420 ph\u00fat \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2017/18 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Leicester, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Premier League. Harry Maguire trung b\u00ecnh 4.63 \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n, 3.26 l\u1ea7n t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 4.3 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao Leicester \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5241","checkdouble":"194042"},{"date":"17:02 08/08","title":"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea 0-0 (pen 5-4) Lyon","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-dau-chelsea-00-lyon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac gi\u1ea3i ICC v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Lyon t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge. \u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Sarri ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa ch\u1ec9 r\u00f5 nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a The Blues. Sau \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><h2>Chelsea ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 Sarri-ball\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea 0-0 Lyon h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea 0-0 Lyon h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 t\u1ed1t \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Sarri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Chelsea thi\u1ebfu chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 trong hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Lyon v\u1eeba qua. HLV Sarri s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng \u201ck\u00e9p ph\u1ee5\u201d nh\u01b0 Danny Drinkwater, Tiemoue Bakayoko, Victor Moses hay Tammy Abraham trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Ngo\u00e0i ra, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o nh\u01b0ng Chelsea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Tammy Abraham \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng khi thay th\u1ebf Morata nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 li\u00ean k\u1ebft t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMoses, Drinkwater v\u00e0 Bakayoko t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Chelsea c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i l\u1edbn m\u00f9a t\u1edbi khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin d\u00f9ng. V\u00ec v\u1eady, Sarri \u0111ang g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn v\u1edbi b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 n\u00e1o lo\u1ea1n khi Sarri \u0111\u1ed5i h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea 0-0 (pen 5-4) Lyon h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea 0-0 (pen 5-4) Lyon h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/Nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-dau-Chelsea-0-0-(pen-5-4)-Lyon-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Moses kh\u00f3 gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt 4-3-3 g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Sarri. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0m ph\u00e1t sinh nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u00e0 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n giao h\u1eefu v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 r\u00f5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVictor Moses t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh trong vai tr\u00f2 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng bi\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Conte. Nh\u01b0ng trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Sarri, Moses s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n trong vai tr\u00f2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nigeria kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho vai tr\u00f2 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0o tay Willian.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDavide Zappacosta c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e0ng l\u00e0m cho kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Moses c\u00e0ng gi\u1ea3m s\u00fat. M\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng bi\u00ean kh\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Conte l\u00e0 Marcos Alonso c\u0169ng m\u1edbi b\u1ecb chi\u1ebfm m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u1edfi Emerson Palmieri do kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, c\u00e1c trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i d\u1ea7n th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i 3. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t khi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.</div>\r\n<h2>L\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Chelsea c\u00f3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u01a1n v\u1edbi Sarri\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea 0-0 (pen 5-4) Lyon h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea 0-0 (pen 5-4) Lyon h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/Nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-dau-Chelsea-0-0-(pen-5-4)-Lyon-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Ampadu c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng v\u01b0\u01a1n xa d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u00ecu d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Sarri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Maurizio Sarri th\u01b0\u1eddng \u00edt ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Napoli c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1ec9 cao th\u1ee9 5 t\u1ea1i Serie A. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi 91 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa so\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Juventus. Napoli c\u0169ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 90 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh Scudetto.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u01b0 Ethan Ampadu, Callum Hudson-Odoi hay Marcin Bulka \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ti\u1ec1n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. V\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri t\u1ea1o ra ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Video tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea 0-0 Lyon (Giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018):</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/8/CHELSEA-VS-LYON.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hazard-va-giroud-muon-chelsea-mua-nabil-fekir-172-194029.html\">Hazard v\u00e0 Giroud mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sarri-hua-hen-giup-chelsea-choi-tot-trong-3-thang-172-194027.html\">Sarri h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n gi\u00fap Chelsea ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong 3 th\u00e1ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5240","checkdouble":"194043"},{"date":"17:38 08/08","title":"Kepa Arrizabalaga \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Courtois?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/8/kepa-arrizabalaga-co-du-kha-nang-thay-the-vi-tri-do-courtois-de-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Kepa Arrizabalaga t\u1eeb Athletic Bilbao v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Alisson \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. C\u00f9ng so s\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00fat ra k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn Kepa c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Courtois \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i hay kh\u00f4ng?\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Courtois quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef Thibaut Courtois \u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge. Trong khi nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a The Blues nh\u01b0 Hazard, Kante v\u00e0 Giroud \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau qu\u00e3ng ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf World Cup 2018 th\u00ec Courtois v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u1edf B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Kepa Arrizabalaga c\u1ee7a Bilbao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Kepa Arrizabalaga c\u1ee7a Bilbao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Chelsea-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-Kepa-Arrizabalaga-cua-Bilbao-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Courtois quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd Express c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea b\u1edfi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Real Madrid. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Courtois th\u00ec n\u00e0i n\u1ec9 Chelsea bu\u00f4ng tha cho th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ea7n g\u0169i c\u00e1c con c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Courtois gia \u0111\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i nh\u01b0ng Chelsea \u0111ang ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng h\u1ecd t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a Courtois&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 Kristof Terreur ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Courtois \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn t\u1edbi Bernabeu. &ldquo;Courtois \u0111ang \u1edf B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 s\u1ebd di chuy\u1ec3n th\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ebfn TBN \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Real. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Los Blancos s\u1ebd s\u1edbm ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn. H\u1ecd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 6 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Courtois, \u1edf Bernabeu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y nh\u1eadn l\u01b0\u01a1ng 300.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n. Chelsea thu v\u1ec1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ch\u1ed1t Kepa Arrizabalaga thay Courtois</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00f4m nay, nh\u1eefng t\u1edd b\u00e1o \u1edf Anh v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"http://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dong-y-chi-71-trieu-bang-mua-kepa-arrizabalaga-172-193984.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa Arrizabalaga</span> c\u1ee7a Athletic Bilbao v\u00e0\u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kepa Arrizabalaga \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Kepa Arrizabalaga \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Kepa-Arrizabalaga-o-dau-khi-so-sanh-voi-Courtois-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kepa</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Bilbao \u0111\u00e3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 23 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Theo \u0111\u00f3 Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Kepa v\u1ec1 Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Bilbao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf London trong 24 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Chelsea.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ebfn 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Kepa, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Alisson (65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, t\u1eeb Roma \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool) \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<h2>Kepa c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thay th\u1ebf Courtois?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng so s\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Kepa v\u1edbi Courtois \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u00fat ra k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn li\u1ec7u anh ch\u00e0ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thay th\u1ebf Courtois hay kh\u00f4ng?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Courtois co the thay the vi tri do Courtois de lai\" title=\"Courtois c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Courtois \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/courtois-6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kepa v\u00e0 Courtois \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, Kepa ra s\u00e2n 26 l\u1ea7n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Bilbao \u1edf La Liga, ch\u1ec9 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00f3 6 tr\u1eadn, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ee9ng 23%. Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Courtois t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u: gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 15/35 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2017/18 (43%).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u00e0n thua, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh 26 tr\u1eadn \u1edf La Liga v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn 36 b\u00e0n thua, Courtois t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 31 b\u00e0n thua nh\u01b0ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn 35 tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Kepa t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, anh c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 80 l\u1ea7n sau 26 tr\u1eadn, trung b\u00ecnh 3.25 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn. Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Courtois ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 61 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 sau 35 tr\u1eadn (trung b\u00ecnh 1.7).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Courtois \u1edf m\u1ee9c 68% c\u00f2n Kepa nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n v\u1edbi 72%. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u m\u1eafc 1 l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua. V\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1eaft d\u00ednh b\u00f3ng, Kepa nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p (79 so v\u1edbi 65).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kepa Arrizabalaga\" title=\"Kepa Arrizabalaga\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/Maurizio-Sarri-phat-bieu-ve-chuyen-nhuong-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kepa Arrizabalaga ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Courtois \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1eaft b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng, Kepa c\u00f3 3,86 l\u1ea7n x\u1eed l\u00fd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng/tr\u1eadn, th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Courtois l\u00e0 4,23. M\u1edbi 23 tu\u1ed5i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng. 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Chelsea chi ra l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 nh\u1ecf, nh\u01b0ng Kepa \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9ng minh r\u1eb1ng anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf t\u1ed1t Courtois.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5239","checkdouble":"194047"},{"date":"11:08 08/08","title":"\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau tin \u0111\u1ed3n\" xinh t\u01b0\u01a1i c\u1ed5 v\u0169 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-1 U23 Uzbekistan","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/nguoi-yeu-tin-don-xinh-tuoi-co-vu-tien-dao-van-duc-tran-u23-viet-nam-11-u23-uzbekistan.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"5238","checkdouble":"194018"}]}